---
/**
 * rest-api/0003 · Figure 4 — "what you actually engineer": at-least-once delivery
 * + idempotent processing = exactly-once EFFECT (not exactly-once delivery).
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from the source HTML (figure + svg + figcaption). Lives as an
 * .astro component for the kebab-case-SVG reason. References no arrow markers, so
 * no local <defs> is needed. (Note the inline <em> inside an SVG <text>; kept as
 * authored.)
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 130"
        role="img"
        aria-label="At-least-once delivery plus idempotent processing equals exactly-once effect, not exactly-once delivery"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="320"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">WHAT YOU ACTUALLY ENGINEER</text
            >
            <rect x="8" y="38" width="180" height="52" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></rect>
            <text x="98" y="60" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="700"
                >at-least-once delivery</text
            >
            <text x="98" y="77" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >retry until acknowledged</text
            >
            <text x="200" y="70" text-anchor="middle" font-size="22" fill="#7a1f12">+</text>
            <rect x="218" y="38" width="180" height="52" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></rect>
            <text x="308" y="60" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="700"
                >idempotent processing</text
            >
            <text x="308" y="77" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >dedup on the receiver</text
            >
            <text x="410" y="70" text-anchor="middle" font-size="22" fill="#7a1f12">=</text>
            <rect
                x="428"
                y="38"
                width="204"
                height="52"
                rx="9"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="530"
                y="60"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">exactly-once EFFECT</text
            >
            <text x="530" y="77" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >delivered many times, takes effect once</text
            >
            <text x="320" y="118" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" fill="#9a2417"
                >✗ Exactly-once <em>delivery</em> is impossible in a distributed system — don't claim
                it.</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Pair retries with <strong>exponential backoff + jitter</strong> and honour <code
            >Retry-After</code
        >; only retry operations that are idempotent.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
